@wp.kernel
def expr_wjcphp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.34)) / wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs((tmp + 0.69 - v1 + 0.36)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.77) + 0.56) * tmp)
    v0 = v2
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v1 + 0.64 - v0 + 0.44)))
    v0 = wp.exp(v0)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp((v0 + 0.63 + tmp + 0.33)))
    tmp = 0.47
    data[tid] = v0
